title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Aug 13 2021

description:
PODCAST SUMMARY HOUR 3: Border patrol agents say crossings are the highest they have ever been. DHS Secretary says border crisis "unsustainable," "we are going to lose" in leaked audio. Between the border, Afghanistan, covid insanity, mask mandates, inflation, gas prices: What has the Biden team done well? The MLB's Field of Dreams was a smash hit. Pro or con on Kevin Costner? Longmire or Yellowstone? It's movie Friday!
